                  </hi>. I am single. I know the prisoner and James Simms—I have frequenbtly seen them together—Mallett reprosenteed himself as Simm's brtoher and said he was a watchmaker—on Saturday, the 6th of Febraury, 1836, they were both at my house to tea—I am quite sure of that—they both by the name of Collier.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> What makes you recollect the day? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> It was the day Simms was apprehended.</p>
